  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The aim of this project is to ensure continuation of leprosy services in Sirajganj, Pabna &amp; Natore Districts. The aim of this project is to ensure continuation of leprosy services in Sirajganj, Pabna &amp; Natore Districts. During the gap period between the end of the TB Control NFM Project and the start of the CLHSS 3rd Phase, the bridge project will initiate a Health System Strengthening (HSS) model focusing on government health personnel capacity building, advocacy, communication and monitoring of the program. This initiative will be able to continue leprosy control with low resources and a minimum number of staff in order to support integrated leprosy services from the Upazila Health Centre.</narrative>
  </description>
